trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of instances of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> class.
This class cannot be inherited.

The <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart> class corresponds to a Web Services Description Language (WSDL) `<part>` element enclosed by the `<message>` element, which is in turn enclosed by the `<definitions>` root element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart>類別會對應至 Web 服務描述語言 (WSDL)`<part>`元素括住`<message>`項目，接著括在`<definitions>`根項目。

trans-unit.source: For more information about WSDL, see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: 如需有關 WSDL 的詳細資訊，請參閱規格的http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the use of the methods and properties exposed by the `MessagePartCollection` class.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範如何使用的方法和屬性所公開`MessagePartCollection`類別。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> to add to the collection.
Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePartCollection" />.
The zero-based index where the <paramref name="messagePart" /> parameter has been added.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> for which to check collection membership.
Returns a value indicating whether the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> is a member of the <see langword="MessagePartCollection" />.

<see langword="true" /> if the <paramref name="messagePart" /> parameter is a member of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePartCollection" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
The following example demonstrates a use of the `Contains` method.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範使用`Contains`方法。

trans-unit.source: An array of type <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> serving as the destination of the copy action.
The zero-based index at which to start placing the copied collection.

Copies the entire <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePartCollection" /> to a compatible one-dimensional array of type <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" />, starting at the specified zero-based index of the target array.
The following example demonstrates a use of the `CopyTo` method.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範使用`CopyTo`方法。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> for which to search in the collection.
Searches for the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> and returns the zero-based index of the first occurrence within the collection.
A 32-bit signed integer.
The following example demonstrates a use of the `IndexOf` method to determine whether a specified `MessagePart` is a member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範使用`IndexOf`方法，以判斷是否指定`MessagePart`集合的成員。

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to insert the <c>messagePart</c> parameter.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> to add to the collection.
Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePartCollection" /> at the specified zero-based index.
If the number of items in the collection already equals the collection's capacity, the capacity is doubled by automatically reallocating the internal array before the new element is inserted.
trans-unit.target: 如果已經在集合中的項目數等於集合的容量，容量加倍插入新項目之前，會自動重新配置內部的陣列。

trans-unit.source: If the `index` parameter is equal to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, the `messagePart` parameter is added to the end of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePartCollection>.
trans-unit.target: 如果`index`參數等於<xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>、`messagePart`參數加入至結尾<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePartCollection>。

trans-unit.source: The elements after the insertion point move down to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: 向下移動以容納新項目插入點後的項目。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> specified by the parameter passed in.
The zero-based index of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> whose value is modified or returned.
Gets or sets the value of a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> at the specified zero-based index.
A <see langword="MessagePart" />.
The following example demonstrates the use of a zero-based index to iterate through the members of a `MessagePartCollection`.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範如何使用以零為起始的索引來逐一查看的成員`MessagePartCollection`。

trans-unit.source: The name of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> returned.
Gets a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> specified by its name.
A <see langword="MessagePart" />.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> to remove from the collection.
Removes the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> from the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePartCollection" />.
This method performs a linear search; therefore, the average execution time is proportional to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 這個方法會執行線性搜尋;因此，平均執行時間是成比例<xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>。

trans-unit.source: The elements that follow the removed <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart> move up to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: 請依照下列所移除的項目<xref:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart>向上移動以佔用空出的位置。
